#: src/big_parental_controls/ui/compliance.py:27
msgid "Enable Activity Monitoring"
msgstr ""
#: src/big_parental_controls/ui/compliance.py:30
#, python-format
msgid ""
"By enabling monitoring for %(user)s, the following data will be collected "
"and stored exclusively on this device:\n"
"\n"
"Data collected:\n"
"• Names of applications used (checked every 60 seconds)\n"
"• Duration of use per application\n"
"• Login and logout times\n"
"\n"
"Data controller: You (the device administrator).\n"
"Purpose: Child safety monitoring.\n"
"Legal basis: Parental consent (LGPD Art. 14, GDPR Art. 8, ECA Digital Art. "
